---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Autonomy Bridge — Decision-Grade Research for AI, Robotics & Industrial Automation"
  description="Autonomy Bridge provides decision-grade research for AI, robotics, industrial automation, and enterprise B2B SaaS, so leaders can make high-stakes calls with evidence, not assumption."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="container">
    <h1>When advanced technology meets market reality, most decisions fail.</h1>

    <p class="subhead">
      Autonomy Bridge provides decision-grade research for AI, robotics, industrial automation,
      and enterprise B2B SaaS — so leaders can make high-stakes calls with evidence, not assumption.
    </p>

    <section class="home-decisions">
      <h2>Decisions Autonomy Bridge helps answer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Is this AI or robotics opportunity commercially viable?</li>
        <li>Is there enterprise demand beyond pilots?</li>
        <li>What pricing and business model will clear the market?</li>
        <li>What adoption risks will block scale?</li>
        <li>Should this be pursued, paused, or stopped?</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="home-intro">
      <p>
        Autonomy Bridge is a principal-led boutique research firm operating at the intersection
        of advanced technology and enterprise adoption. The firm focuses on markets where technical
        feasibility does not guarantee commercial success.
      </p>
      <p>
        The firm exists to bridge the gap between technical capability and market reality.
        Engagements focus on clarity, not optimism.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/research">See how we work →</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
